      <h1>Website Design Tips for Local Businesses in 2025</h1>
      <p class="article-meta">
        <strong>Published:</strong> November 24, 2025 •
        <strong>Reading Time:</strong> 7 minutes
      </p>

      <p>
        Design a fast, clear, and conversion-focused website that helps local
